reviews.review_text: Possibly best show of 1990 Yeah, I know, 3-29 with Branford, 7-12, 9-20, 12-31, but this one's right up there with them.  This show doesn't have a Dark Star, but it has incredible play and a challenging, fun, jam-packed setlist from beginning to end.  This audience tape is about as good as it gets after about 2:30 when they turn up Brent.  A true gem.
